**Distinguishing real meetings from work blocks:**
- Self-created event + 1 attendee + no Zoom/Meet link = **work block placeholder** (protected work time, not a commitment)
- Multiple attendees or external organizer = **real meeting/commitment**
- Events with Zoom/Meet links = **real meeting** even if few attendees

